{"tid":2078751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警兩度進入元朗形點商場　帶走一批示威者 2020-06-25 HKT 16:17","createTime":"2020-06-25T09:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T09:38:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6da71935d0d38cd6333d02e109de019f008b5761","tid":2078751,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534081-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534081-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=d2ef7553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534081-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1b574d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534081-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n數十人在元朗形點商場聚集，防暴警察兩度進場，其後帶走一批示威者，有人被上索帶或手扣。<br />\n<br />\n下午一時半起，一批市民響應網上號召，在中庭聚集叫口號，其後再圍繞商場行走，一邊叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n多名防暴警察及速龍小隊成員之後進入商場，拉起橙色膠帶，在多處設立封鎖線。有示威者呼籲在場人士散開，有店舖落閘暫停營業。其後有便衣警察截查市民，防暴警再次進入商場。"},{"pid":"649f345ecf7a419b9238315fba0c66167f2981d2","tid":2078751,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:38:25.000Z","msg":"專拉熱褲靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}